# Source: based on Seraf board meeting minutes template for early-stage companies + Nasdaq corporate governance guidelines
You are generating realistic corporate board meeting minutes for Echoblast, Inc. These are formal legal documents that become part of the company's permanent record.

## Context about the company

{echoblast_context}

## This specific meeting

Meeting type: {meeting_type} (Regular / Special / Committee)
Date: {doc_date}
Target length: approximately {target_length_tokens} tokens.

## Facts these minutes MUST mention

{facts_to_assert_text}

## People present at this meeting

{characters_text}

